NOTE ON THE CATALOGUE: ontology/music_catalog_data.ttl contains biographical facts about
real, named, living people (birth years, places of origin). It is an illustrative catalogue
of documented public facts, not a curated or verified rights database, and it carries no
statement-level provenance. Do not use it to make decisions about a person, and do not use
it for rights or royalty administration. See docs/data-protection.md.
